{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 437645, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "党员就一定有坚定的马克思主义信仰了吗", "timestamp": 1602425548, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437649, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在入党的过程中接受考验、在入党之后丰富的生产生活学习工作实践中接受考验、用生命历程检验马克思主义信仰的正确性和科学性（", "timestamp": 1602425656, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437654, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "早年间朴素的爱国主义情感+家人党员的影响+2018-19年前后996事件和隔壁鹿会事件的一些思考", "timestamp": 1602425698, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437658, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "毛选，好好读", "timestamp": 1602425764, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437659, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz觉得是不是需要先有坚定的信仰然后才去入党比较好", "timestamp": 1602425782, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437660, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 能具体谈谈思考嘛qwq dz虽然会关注某些社会热点话题，但不太擅长用比较严肃、理论的方式思考和表达", "timestamp": 1602425834, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437661, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 啊我可能没说清楚 我就是想问入党前如何树立信仰", "timestamp": 1602425871, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437663, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 感觉光凭党课和党课小组的一些活动，dz还是有点无感，但是有可能的话还是挺想树立信仰的", "timestamp": 1602425955, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437676, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本来听某领导讲党怎么怎么好还觉得入党很光荣，但了解了那个领导的不光彩过去之后，啧啧啧啧，不过如此，不过如此", "timestamp": 1602426192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437679, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 还是结合实践深入了解党和党员吧，多说无益", "timestamp": 1602426253, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437681, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 读读近代史和党史，可能会有点用？", "timestamp": 1602426263, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437687, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 要多读书，书里什么都写了。去读马克思的《雇佣劳动与资本》，搞明白剩余价值是怎么一回事，然后就知道996的本质是什么，某些大公司企图掩盖的是什么。", "timestamp": 1602426359, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437695, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "知乎之前有个答主叫 玄不救非氪不改命，人称玄处，现在已经被封了，看他的系列文章逐渐长得姿势", "timestamp": 1602426527, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437702, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "多读一读相关书籍，资本论，毛选", "timestamp": 1602426642, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437709, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 玄处应该还在新潮沉思录上活动", "timestamp": 1602426848, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437710, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 那都过时了，和四书五经没差别", "timestamp": 1602426881, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437711, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "摇头晃脑地毛曰马曰顶个屁用", "timestamp": 1602426901, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437714, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 您读过马毛还是读过四书五经？", "timestamp": 1602427034, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437717, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 四书五经五卷毛选资本论共产党宣言我都读过", "timestamp": 1602427160, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437720, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "多了解一些历史与政治知识，关注社会现实以及时事，然后阅读马克思主义著作时产生了共鸣。", "timestamp": 1602427192, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437722, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 不解决问题啊，都是过时的东西，一百多年前和两千多年前的人说的话，能直接拿来用？", "timestamp": 1602427199, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437747, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "加入tcp吧", "timestamp": 1602427804, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437812, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 划重点，“直接”二字，我们主张读书并不代表就要直接用他们说过的话，直接用肯定不现实，但你能否定读这些书的价值么", "timestamp": 1602428789, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437834, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 这些书是价值论的书，很少涉及方法论，对于信的人当然有价值，但是这和入不入党没关系，现在都学新思想啦", "timestamp": 1602429084, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437903, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我喜欢过勇老师，所以想入党吧", "timestamp": 1602429935, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 437955, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 90817, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "父母是下岗工人，从小随